Package org.antfarmer.ejce.stream

Streaming wrapper classes used to encrypt and compress data.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EncryptInputStream
    Extension of CipherInputStream that transmits the given cipher's initialization vector (if any) at the beginning of the stream.
    GZIPCompressionStream
    An InputStream wrapper that compresses the data within the given InputStream.
